title: Madison Watkins from Year of the Knife and Candy Corpse
itunes:title: Madison Watkins from Year of the Knife and Candy Corpse
description:
I don't think I will ever get tired of a solid metal core record, and Year of The Knife have released exactly that with Internal Incarceration so in turn, I had to have Madison Watkins from the band on the podcast. Madison and I discuss life in Delaware, straight edge and running a small business (with her amazing Candy Corpse brand). It was an absolute pleasure having her on so sit back and enjoy.
